    "Section 3.1).",
    "Models We train all of our models from Gemma-2b-base (Gemma et al., 2024) and LLaMa-3-8Bbase (AI@Meta, 2024).",
    "These models are pre-trained with trillions of tokens from the web, and highly performant for a wide range of text generation tasks (Beeching et al., 2023).",
    "We denote our models trained after each phase as -lion-sft, -liondpo, and -lion-odpo, representing the SFT, offline DPO, and online DPO stages, respectively.",
    "Baselines We mainly compare our method against the officially released instruct models, Gemma-2b-it and Llama-3-8b-it."
